 girl who is about 16 or 17 years old and apprehended him while having carnal knowledge of the victim. “They were three of them who attempted act, but the others saw our men and escaped but the Uche who was already having carnal knowledge of the girl was caught.” However, Public Relations Officer of the state police command, SP. Nnamdi Omoni, who confirmed the incident, noted that the Commissioner of Police in Rivers state, Joseph Mukan had ordered the matter be transferred to the State Criminal Investigative Department for investigation. Vanguard News Nigeria. ...They video recorded the moment as they stripped me, inserted fingers in my body -Victim By Egufe Yafugborhi - Port Harcourt Police in Rivers State on Friday disclosed the arrest of an eight-man vigilante team in Diobu, Port Harcourt for alleged rape and kidnapping. The arrest followed the report by… April 24, 2020 In "Metro" By Egufe Yafugborhi - Port Harcourt Police in Rivers State on Friday disclosed the arrest of an eight-man vigilante team in Diobu, Port Harcourt for alleged rape and kidnapping. The arrest followed the report by a 21-year-old girl (name withheld) who told the police that the 8 suspects of the… April 24, 2020 In "Metro" PORT HARCOURT — POLICE have arrested members of a 15-man gang that allegedly raped a 16-year-old girl in Gbuga area of Ogbunabali, Port Harcourt, Rivers State. June 27, 2014 In "News"